PP_URLREQUESTPROPERTY_FOLLOWREDIRECTS,      // PP_Bool (default=PP_TRUE)
http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/ppapi/c/ppb_url_request_info.h?revision=72960&amp;content-type=text/plain

Cross origin failures do indeed correspond to NOACCESS (-7). They are not allowed by Chrome.
http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/ppapi/c/pp_errors.h?revision=73683&amp;content-type=text/plain

